1
00:00:00,708 --> 00:00:05,195
Can't you come in and have tea now, Peter?
Peter,你不能现在进来喝茶吗?

2
00:00:05,478 --> 00:00:07,193
Not yet.
还不能.

3
00:00:08,108 --> 00:00:11,498
I must water the garden first.
我得先给花园浇水.

4
00:00:11,499 --> 00:00:15,014
Do you have to water it now?
你一定得现在浇吗?

5
00:00:15,034 --> 00:00:17,328
I'm afraid I must.
恐怕我得现在浇.

6
00:00:17,329 --> 00:00:19,325
Look at it!
你看看它,

7
00:00:19,326 --> 00:00:21,786
It's terribly dry.
干得厉害.

8
00:00:21,787 --> 00:00:24,109
What a nuisance!
真是个麻烦事!

9
00:00:24,382 --> 00:00:28,585
Last summer it was very dry, too.
去年夏天它也是干得很.

10
00:00:28,586 --> 00:00:30,360
Don't you remember?
你不记得了吗?

11
00:00:30,841 --> 00:00:34,366
I had to water it every day.
我不得不每天浇水.

12
00:00:34,453 --> 00:00:39,008
Well, I'll have tea by myself.
好吧,我一个人喝茶了.

13
00:00:39,009 --> 00:00:41,022
That was quick!
好快啊!

14
00:00:41,258 --> 00:00:44,462
Have you finished already?
你已经浇完了?

15
00:00:44,878 --> 00:00:48,057
Yes. Look out of the window.
是的.你看看窗外.

16
00:00:48,132 --> 00:00:50,033
It's raining!
下雨了!

17
00:00:50,956 --> 00:00:55,844
That means You don't need to water the garden.
那就是说,你不必给花园浇水了.

18
00:00:56,114 --> 00:00:59,131
That was a pleasant surprise.
那是个令人愉快的惊喜.

19
00:00:59,363 --> 00:01:02,854
It means I can have tea, instead.
这意味着我可以喝茶了.

